snippet.title: Divya, IAS, Rank 105 | UPSC Topper 2022  | Hindi Medium | Mock Interview | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Divya has secured 105th rank in UPSC CSE exam 2022. The mock interview she has given in Drishti IAS institute has been uploaded on Drishti IAS Channel. We extend our heartiest congratulations to Divya on this great achievement. We feel immense pleasure to be a part of her beautiful journey and once again we wish her all the very best for a bright future.
As we all know that UPSC CSE Mock Interviews are a great medium to understand the various dimensions of the Personality Test conducted by UPSC. These Mock Interviews not only familiarize the aspirants with the actual process of UPSC Interviews but also help in identifying the areas that a candidate needs to work upon. Even though one can imagine oneself in a UPSC Interview setting, it is strongly recommended that you watch these Mock Interviews and learn from the experiences of IAS toppers, so that you give your best shot when you reach the interview stage of examination.
We hope that this video of the UPSC IAS Mock Interview will help you understand the approach one should have to tackle the various kinds of questions asked by the panel members.

Even though one can imagine oneself in a UPSC Interview setting, it is strongly recommended that you watch these Mock Interviews and learn from the experiences of IAS toppers, so that you give your best shot when you reach the interview stage of examination.
We hope that this video of the UPSC IAS Mock Interview will help you understand the approach one should have to tackle the various kinds of questions asked by the panel members.

Tere Bin Episode 49 Teaser - 25th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: PART 2 - RAHUL DUA IN AMERICA | The HORRORS of RENTING a CAR in USA | StandUp Comedy by Rahul Dua
snippet.description:
"Oh Hello!" Australia and NZ tour (Jun'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour
"New Comedy Special 2023-24" UK-EU Tour (Aug-Sep'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour

This video is the 2nd and the most important part of my series of jokes and observations about life in USA. 
These are observational jokes rehearsed and delivered in just 8 - 9 shows, unlike conventional stand up content which takes a couple of years to perfect. 
Since public transport is nearly absent in USA, I had to rent a car to move around. Though bad, it was the one way. This video is a real life personal account of me renting American Muscle and the horrors associated with it. Via this video I hope to convey all of my anger, surprise, shock, regret and the plethora of other emotions that I felt arising out of the massive inconvenience and hidden charges associated with US Car rental. 
Drop in a LIKE and SHARE the video if you've had similar experiences or know someone who went through something similar, and COMMENT with your favourite joke from the video. 

#rahuldua #usa #standupcomedy #nri #comedy #jokes #carrental #taxes #dodge #americanmuscle #story

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 48 Teaser - 24th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: THE FLASH - FINAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
Are YOU ready? THE FLASH - Only in Theaters June 16. #TheFlashMovie

Text 239-932-7332 to join the DC Community.
 https://my.community.com/dc

Warner Bros. Pictures presents ‚ÄúThe Flash,‚Äù directed by Andy Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù). Ezra Miller reprises their role as Barry Allen in the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first-ever standalone feature film.

Worlds collide in ‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù when Barry uses his superpowers to travel back in time in order to change the events of the past. But when his attempt to save his family inadvertently alters the future, Barry becomes trapped in a reality in which General Zod has returned, threatening annihilation, and there are no Super Heroes to turn to. That is, unless Barry can coax a very different Batman out of retirement and rescue an imprisoned Kryptonian‚Ä¶ albeit not the one he‚Äôs looking for. Ultimately, to save the world that he is in and return to the future that he knows, Barry‚Äôs only hope is to race for his life. But will making the ultimate sacrifice be enough to reset the universe?

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù ensemble also includes rising star Sasha Calle, Michael Shannon (‚ÄúBullet Train,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman v Superman: Dawn of Justice‚Äù), Ron Livingston (‚ÄúLoudermilk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Conjuring‚Äù), Maribel Verd√∫ (‚ÄúElite,‚Äù ‚ÄúY tu mam√° tambi√©n‚Äù), Kiersey Clemons (‚ÄúZack Snyder‚Äôs Justice League,‚Äù ‚ÄúSweetheart‚Äù), Antje Traue (‚ÄúKing of Ravens,‚Äù ‚ÄúMan of Steel‚Äù) and Michael Keaton (‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman‚Äù).

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù is produced by Barbara Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù) and Michael Disco (‚ÄúRampage,‚Äù ‚ÄúSan Andreas‚Äù). The screenplay is by Christina Hodson (‚ÄúBirds of Prey,‚Äù ‚ÄúBumblebee‚Äù), with a screen story by John Francis Daley & Jonathan Goldstein (‚ÄúDungeons & Dragons: Honor Among Thieves,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming‚Äù) and Joby Harold (‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts,‚Äù ‚ÄúArmy of the Dead‚Äù), based on characters from DC. The executive producers are Toby Emmerich, Walter Hamada, Galen Vaisman and Marianne Jenkins.

Joining director Muschietti behind the camera are director of photography Henry Braham (‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), production designer Paul Denham Austerberry (‚ÄúIT Chapter Two,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Shape of Water‚Äù), editors Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby‚Äù) and Paul Machliss (‚ÄúThe Gentlemen,‚Äù ‚ÄúBaby Driver‚Äù), and costume designer Alexandra Byrne (‚ÄúDoctor Strange,‚Äù ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù); the score is by Benjamin Wallfisch (‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures presents a Double Dream/a Disco Factory production of an Andy Muschietti film, ‚ÄúThe Flash.‚Äù It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in theaters in North America on June 16, 2023 and internationally beginning 14 June 2023.

Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. snippet.description:
Get ready to groove to the beats of the latest track 'Baby Tujhe Paap Lagega' from the upcoming movie 'Zara Hatke Zara Bachke' starring Vicky Kaushal and Sara Ali Khan. This catchy number is sure to get you tapping your feet and singing along!

Song Name - Baby Tujhe Paap Lagega
Singer - Himesh Reshammiya , Sachin- Jigar
Music - Sachin- Jigar

Music Production Head - Romil Ved
Mix & Mastered By Eric Pillai @ FSOB Studios

snippet.title: Tere Vaaste | Zara Hatke Zara Bachke | Vicky Kaushal, Sara Ali Khan, Varun J, Sachin-Jigar,Amitabh B
snippet.description:
#TereVaaste is here and it's sure to tug at your heartstrings starring Vicky Kaushal and Sara Ali Khan.

The song has been sung by four talented voices - Varun Jain, Sachin- Jigar, Shadab Faridi, and Altamash Faridi. If that wasn't enough to make you fall in love with the track, wait till you hear the soulful music composed by Sachin-Jigar and lyrics crafted by Amitabh Bhattacharya.

Credits:

Singer - Varun Jain, Sachin- Jigar, Shadab Faridi, Altamash Faridi
Music - Sachin- Jigar
Lyrics - Amitabh Bhattacharya
Programmed & Arranged By - Sachin- Jigar
Additional Programming - Hrishikesh Gangan
Music Production Head - Romil Ved
Live instruments -
Guitar: Indrajit Chetia
Backing Vocals / Chorus-
Rana Majumdar, Hrishikesh Kamerkar
Mix & Mastered By Eric Pillai - FSOB Studios
Assistant Mix Engineer- Michael Edwin Pillai
Recording Engineer - Swar Mehta - White Noise studio

Lyrics:

(Tere vaaste falak se main chaand laaunga

Solah satrah sitaare sang baandh laaunga) √ó 2

Chaand taaron se kaho
Abhi thehrein zara
Chaand taaron se kaho
KI abhi thehrein zara

Pehle ishq lada lun uske baad laaunga
Pehle ishq lada lun uske baad laaunga

Janaab-e-aali
Janaab-e-aali
Hum se mohabbat hai
janaab-e-aali

Janaab-e-aali

Toh ik hidaayat hai
Janaab-e-aali

Apne toh saare paise

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is here to entertain and make you all laugh once again! Watch the characters try to live their day-to-day lives and in return make everyone on a laughter ride! Watch these specially curated clips and relax.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ  #SonyPAL

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Reprise | Music Prod. by @BluishMusic
snippet.description:
"Boyfriend Reprise" the song offers a raw and honest plea of running away from toxicity, own thoughts, insecure nature of an individual in a relationship. This reprise version is a nonchalant expression of Dino James wherein through his powerful lyrics and emotional delivery, Dino James sheds light on an important issue that is often overlooked and ignored in our society. Dino James has a strong message for the ones who are facing such insecurities, "You shouldn't let such insecurities consume you or bother you choose to walk away and cut-off this insecurities when needed"

Dino James has a strong message for the ones who are facing such insecurities, "You shouldn't let such insecurities consume you or bother you choose to walk away and cut-off this insecurities when needed"

snippet.description:
Brahmanandam Super Comedy Scene | Soggadu Telugu Movie | SP Shorts

Soggadu is a 2005 Indian Telugu-language romance film produced by D. Suresh on Suresh Productions banner. Directed by Ravi Babu, it stars Tarun and Aarthi Agarwal in lead roles. With special appearances by Venkatesh, Srikanth , Shriya Saran and Sumanth. Soggadu won good critical appreciation and technical acclaim for the director Ravi Babu. This film was remade in Hindi as Ajab Prem Ki Ghazab Kahani (2009) and in Bengali as Mon Je Kore Uru Uru (2010).

Directed by :  Ravi Babu
Written by  :      Nivas (dialogues)
Screenplay by :  Paruchuri Brothers
Story by :  Ravi Babu
Produced by : D. Suresh Babu,  D. Rama Naidu (presents)
Starring          : Tarun, Aarthi Agarwal, Jugal Hansraj
Cinematography :  Loganathan Srinivasan
Edited by :  Anthony
Music by :  Chakri
Production Company : Suresh Productions
Release date :  31 March 2005

snippet.description:
Cheetah ‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡•å‡§§ ‡§ï‡§æ ‡§ï‡•à‡§∏‡•á ‡§¨‡§¶‡§≤‡§æ ‡§≤‡•á‡§ó‡•Ä Karishma Singh || Maddam Sir - Ep.124

Show Name ‚Äì Maddam Sir
Star Cast ‚Äì Gulki Joshi, Shilpa Shinde, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Produced By ‚Äì Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir #‡§Æ‡•à‡§°‡•ç‡§°‡§Æ‡§∏‡§∞ #comedy 

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences that add to the drama madam and comedy

snippet.title: The Sengol, the eternal symbol of transfer of power to India in 1947
snippet.description:
At the inauguration of the new Parliament House on 28th May 2023, PM Narendra Modi will establish the historical and sacred 'Sengol' in the Parliament House. It will be installed close to the Speaker‚Äôs podium in the Lok Sabha.

Considered as the symbol of fair and equitable governance, this is the same Sengol that was accepted by the first Prime Minister of India, Jawaharlal Nehru on the night of 14th August. It was precisely the moment in which power was transferred by the British into the hands of Indians.

snippet.title: Journey from IPS to IAS. Divya. Rank- 105 | UPSC Topper 2022 | Hindi Medium | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:

Team Drishti wishes Divya a very successful and fruitful career.

localized.title: Journey from IPS to IAS. Divya. Rank- 105 | UPSC Topper 2022 | Hindi Medium | Drishti IAS
localized.description:
Divya has secured 105th rank in the Civil Services Examination 2022. In this video Divya is sharing her experience of preparation. She is also giving an important strategy for the upcoming CSE exam 2023. This video will definitely motivate you.

Team Drishti wishes Divya a very successful and fruitful career.

Episode 3779: Unlucky Name
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha recommends numerous names that begin with the letter "P" but Popatlal deems them dated. Jetha inadvertently recommends the name of Russian President Putin, which Popatlal definitely cannot use. Last but not least, Bawri recommends the name "Pyare," which everyone adores. Popatlal's name has been changed, and he will now be known as Pyarelal, according to Bhide. Madhavi calls Vinu Kaka to confirm the new name, and he suggests that it is a good name for Popatlal. Will Popatlal, aka Pyarelal, marry following this name change?

snippet.description:

A bunch of people are invited to play some mysterious game. Called in a mysterious house, every individual gets an envelope that consists of further instructions about the game. One of the participants, Rohit, gets the blank envelope and is feeling confused. A mysterious voice, which earlier guided the contestants, is heard again by Rohit who helps him procure a gun. Rohit gets the instructions of attacking someone. Who is that person? What is this game? Can CID solve this case? To know, watch the full episode.

#CID #‡§∏‡•Ä‡§Ü‡§à‡§°‡•Ä #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID #setindia 

About CID:
-----------------
Today, the first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. The plot throws up intriguing twists and turns at every stage to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: THE FLASH - FINAL TRAILER - OFFICIAL WARNER BROS. UK & IRELAND
snippet.description:
Are YOU ready? Watch the new trailer for #TheFlashMovie, in cinemas June 14.

Warner Bros. Pictures presents ‚ÄúThe Flash,‚Äù directed by Andy Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù). Ezra Miller reprises their role as Barry Allen in the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first-ever standalone feature film.

Worlds collide in ‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù when Barry uses his superpowers to travel back in time in order to change the events of the past. But when his attempt to save his family inadvertently alters the future, Barry becomes trapped in a reality in which General Zod has returned, threatening annihilation, and there are no Super Heroes to turn to. That is, unless Barry can coax a very different Batman out of retirement and rescue an imprisoned Kryptonian‚Ä¶ albeit not the one he‚Äôs looking for. Ultimately, to save the world that he is in and return to the future that he knows, Barry‚Äôs only hope is to race for his life. But will making the ultimate sacrifice be enough to reset the universe?

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù ensemble also includes rising star Sasha Calle, Michael Shannon (‚ÄúBullet Train,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman v Superman: Dawn of Justice‚Äù), Ron Livingston (‚ÄúLoudermilk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Conjuring‚Äù), Maribel Verd√∫ (‚ÄúElite,‚Äù ‚ÄúY tu mam√° tambi√©n‚Äù), Kiersey Clemons (‚ÄúZack Snyder‚Äôs Justice League,‚Äù ‚ÄúSweetheart‚Äù), Antje Traue (‚ÄúKing of Ravens,‚Äù ‚ÄúMan of Steel‚Äù) and Michael Keaton (‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman‚Äù).

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù is produced by Barbara Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù) and Michael Disco (‚ÄúRampage,‚Äù ‚ÄúSan Andreas‚Äù). The screenplay is by Christina Hodson (‚ÄúBirds of Prey,‚Äù ‚ÄúBumblebee‚Äù), with a screen story by John Francis Daley & Jonathan Goldstein (‚ÄúDungeons & Dragons: Honor Among Thieves,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming‚Äù) and Joby Harold (‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts,‚Äù ‚ÄúArmy of the Dead‚Äù), based on characters from DC. The executive producers are Toby Emmerich, Walter Hamada, Galen Vaisman and Marianne Jenkins.

Joining director Muschietti behind the camera are director of photography Henry Braham (‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), production designer Paul Denham Austerberry (‚ÄúIT Chapter Two,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Shape of Water‚Äù), editors Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby‚Äù) and Paul Machliss (‚ÄúThe Gentlemen,‚Äù ‚ÄúBaby Driver‚Äù), and costume designer Alexandra Byrne (‚ÄúDoctor Strange,‚Äù ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù); the score is by Benjamin Wallfisch (‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures presents a Double Dream/a Disco Factory production of an Andy Muschietti film, ‚ÄúThe Flash.‚Äù It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in theaters in North America on June 16, 2023 and internationally beginning 14 June 2023.

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù ensemble also includes rising star Sasha Calle, Michael Shannon (‚ÄúBullet Train,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman v Superman: Dawn of Justice‚Äù), Ron Livingston (‚ÄúLoudermilk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Conjuring‚Äù), Maribel Verd√∫ (‚ÄúElite,‚Äù ‚ÄúY tu mam√° tambi√©n‚Äù), Kiersey Clemons (‚ÄúZack Snyder‚Äôs Justice League,‚Äù ‚ÄúSweetheart‚Äù), Antje Traue (‚ÄúKing of Ravens,‚Äù ‚ÄúMan of Steel‚Äù) and Michael Keaton (‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman‚Äù).

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù is produced by Barbara Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù) and Michael Disco (‚ÄúRampage,‚Äù ‚ÄúSan Andreas‚Äù). The screenplay is by Christina Hodson (‚ÄúBirds of Prey,‚Äù ‚ÄúBumblebee‚Äù), with a screen story by John Francis Daley & Jonathan Goldstein (‚ÄúDungeons & Dragons: Honor Among Thieves,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming‚Äù) and Joby Harold (‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts,‚Äù ‚ÄúArmy of the Dead‚Äù), based on characters from DC. The executive producers are Toby Emmerich, Walter Hamada, Galen Vaisman and Marianne Jenkins.

Joining director Muschietti behind the camera are director of photography Henry Braham (‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), production designer Paul Denham Austerberry (‚ÄúIT Chapter Two,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Shape of Water‚Äù), editors Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby‚Äù) and Paul Machliss (‚ÄúThe Gentlemen,‚Äù ‚ÄúBaby Driver‚Äù), and costume designer Alexandra Byrne (‚ÄúDoctor Strange,‚Äù ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù); the score is by Benjamin Wallfisch (‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures presents a Double Dream/a Disco Factory production of an Andy Muschietti film, ‚ÄúThe Flash.‚Äù It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in theaters in North America on June 16, 2023 and internationally beginning 14 June 2023.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.
